{"lastModified":1774616990438,"uri":"c::18231584005::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nS/Y FLO is a Lagoon 52 - 2018 built. She is the perfect yacht to enjoy your summer vacation. She has three seating areas (front, aft and flybridge). Her bathing platform is idea for lounging and enjoying cocktails. She has four queen bed cabins all with private facilities. She boosts an array of water toys for fun on the sea. Her chef will prepare your delicious meals.\n\nDiscover Greece....Go with the Flo!","blueprint":{"name":"FLO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::MJZ2GgMXL.png/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b6e6230-b93d-11ef-9ce9-e3cf8f6660f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b36d770-b93d-11ef-a815-ab7ab3f336d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b5c87e0-b93d-11ef-a815-ab7ab3f336d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b740780-b93d-11ef-a815-ab7ab3f336d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b73b960-b93d-11ef-a815-ab7ab3f336d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b74a3c0-b93d-11ef-a815-ab7ab3f336d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b7280e0-b93d-11ef-a815-ab7ab3f336d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b6fe8d0-b93d-11ef-9ce9-e3cf8f6660f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7b499c20-b93d-11ef-a815-ab7ab3f336d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbabc6-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::